  <titles>
    <title type="display">Protecting Taxpayer Dollars from Taliban Theft Act</title>
    <title type="short" as="introduced">Protecting Taxpayer Dollars from Taliban Theft Act</title>
    <title type="official" as="introduced">To direct the Secretary of State and the Administrator of the United States Agency for International Development to promulgate regulations to require all implementing partners receiving foreign assistance funds with activities in Afghanistan to submit a report on any payments or withholdings, including for taxes, fees, duties, and utilities, made to the Taliban, state-owned enterprises, or governing institutions in Afghanistan, and for other purposes.</title>
  </titles>
